---
description: Calendar time and layout logic guarantees
globs: ["src/logic/**/*", "src/components/calendar/**/*", "src/domain/**/*"]
alwaysApply: true
---

- Slot size is 15 minutes.
- Visible range is 06:00-22:00 unless product docs are updated.
- `end` must always be strictly greater than `start`.
- Minimum duration is 15 minutes.
- Persist event times in ISO UTC format.
- All px<->time conversions must use centralized helper functions.
- Event block visual position must match underlying start/end exactly.
- Same input state must produce identical output layout.
